remarks.format:


## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-102">スケール区切りは、グラフの系列のデータ ポイントを再配布に使用されるほとんどの場合、y 軸に意図的な不連続性です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-102">Scale breaks are intentional discontinuities on the Y-axis that are most often used to redistribute the data points in a series on a chart.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-103">この機能は、プロットされる 1 つの系列内のデータの高値と低値に大きな違いがある場合に、読みやすさを向上します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-103">This feature improves readability when there are large differences between the high and low values of the data in one series being plotted.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-104">複数の系列内のデータとの違いについては、スケールの区切り線は描画されません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-104">Scale breaks are not drawn for differences between data in multiple series.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-105">既定では、スケール区切りが無効になります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-105">By default, scale breaks are disabled.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-106">設定して、y 軸のスケール区切りを有効にすることができます、<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.Enabled%2A>プロパティを`true`です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-106">You can enable scale breaks on the Y-axis by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.Enabled%2A> property to `true`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-107">垂直方向のスケール区切りの間隔を変更することを指定する、<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.Spacing%2A>値。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-107">To change the amount of vertical space of the scale break, you can specify a <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.Spacing%2A> value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-108">これは、y 軸のスケールの割合として計算されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-108">This is calculated as a percentage of the Y-axis scale.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-109">スケール区切りを描画する 1 つの系列のデータ ポイントのデータ範囲間の十分な分離が必要です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-109">You must have sufficient separation between ranges of data points in a single series to draw a scale break.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-110">既定では、グラフの 25% 以上のデータ範囲間の分離がある場合にのみ、スケール区切りを追加できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-110">By default, a scale break can be added only if there is a separation between the data ranges of at least 25% of the chart.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-111">スケール区切りを有効にしたが開かない場合は、データ範囲間十分な距離がある場合でも設定できる場合、<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.CollapsibleSpaceThreshold%2A>プロパティを 25 未満の値にします。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-111">If you enable a scale break but it does not appear, even though there is sufficient distance between the data ranges, you can set the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.CollapsibleSpaceThreshold%2A> property to a value less than 25.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-112">グラフは、グラフ; あたり最大 5 つのスケール区切りをサポートします。ただし、グラフは、1 つ以上のスケール区切りを表示する場合にくくなることができます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-112">Charts support up to five scale breaks per chart; however, the chart can become unreadable if you display more than one scale break.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-113">データ範囲が 3 つ以上ある場合は、このデータを表示するための別の方法を使用することを検討します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-113">If you have more than two data ranges, consider using a different method for displaying this data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-114">使用して、<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.MaxNumberOfBreaks%2A>プロパティをグラフに表示できるスケール区切りの数を減らします。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-114">Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.AxisScaleBreakStyle.MaxNumberOfBreaks%2A> property to reduce the number of scale breaks that can be displayed on the chart.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-115">スケール区切りを使用すると、y 軸ラベルをオフセットになる可能性があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-115">When a scale break is used, the Y-axis labels may become offset.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-116">ラベルのオフセットを無効にする設定、<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelStyle.IsStaggered%2A>プロパティを`false`です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-116">To disable the label offset, set the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.LabelStyle.IsStaggered%2A> property to `false`.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-117">スケール区切りは、次の条件のいずれかではサポートされていません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-117">Scale breaks are not supported under any of the following conditions:</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-118">円グラフ、ドーナツ グラフ、じょうごグラフ、ピラミッド、放射状または任意の積み上げグラフの種類が使用されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-118">Pie, doughnut, funnel, pyramid, radial or any stacked chart types are used.</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-119">ラベルのカスタムの間隔、目盛りまたはグリッド線が有効にします。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-119">Custom intervals for labels, tick marks or grid lines are enabled.</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-120">軸の最小値または最大値を設定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-120">The minimum or maximum value for the axis is set.</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-121">カスタム ラベルが使用されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-121">Custom labels are used.</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-122">対数の y 軸を指定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-122">A logarithmic Y-axis is specified.</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-123">スクロールおよびズームを含めるには、軸ビューを y 軸が使用されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-123">Axis views on the Y-axis, which include scrolling and zooming, are used.</span></span>  

-   <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-124">3-D グラフが使用されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-124">3-D charts are used.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="44d9d-125">次のコード例を有効にして、後にスケール区切りをカスタマイズする方法を示しています、<xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>コントロールがデザイン画面に追加されました。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="44d9d-125">The following code example demonstrates how to enable and customize a scale break after the <xref:System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control has been added to the design surface.</span></span>  

```vb  
Imports System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  

Private Function AddChartData()   

    chart1.Series("Default").Points.Add(New DataPoint(1, 2))   
    chart1.Series("Default").Points.Add(New DataPoint(2, 4))   
    chart1.Series("Default").Points.Add(New DataPoint(3, 400000))   
    chart1.Series("Default").Points.Add(New DataPoint(4, 3))   

End Sub  

Private Function AddScaleBreaks()  

   ' Enable scale breaks.  
   chart1.ChartAreas("Default").AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.Enabled = True   

   ' Show scale break if more than 25% of the chart is empty space.       
   chart1.ChartAreas("Default").AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.CollapsibleSpaceThreshold = 25   

   ' Set the line width of the scale break.      
   chart1.ChartAreas("Default").AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.LineWidth = 2   

   ' Set the color of the scale break.   
   chart1.ChartAreas("Default").AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.LineColor = Color.Red   

   ' If all data points are significantly far from zero, the chart will calculate the scale minimum value.   
   chart1.ChartAreas("Default").AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.StartFromZero = StartFromZero.Auto  

   ' Set the spacing gap between the lines of the scale break (as a percentage of the Y-axis).  
   chart1.ChartAreas["Default"].AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.Spacing = 2;  

End Function  
```  

```csharp  
using System.Web.UI.DataVisualization.Charting  

private void AddChartData()  
{  
   chart1.Series["Series1"].Points.Add(new DataPoint(1, 2));  
   chart1.Series["Series1"].Points.Add(new DataPoint(2, 4));  
   chart1.Series["Series1"].Points.Add(new DataPoint(3, 400000));  
   chart1.Series["Series1"].Points.Add(new DataPoint(4, 3));  
}  

private void AddScaleBreaks()  
{  
   // Enable scale breaks.  
   chart1.ChartAreas["ChartArea1"].AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.Enabled = true;  

   // Show scale break if more than 25% of the chart is empty space.  
   chart1.ChartAreas["ChartArea1"].AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.CollapsibleSpaceThreshold = 25;  

   // Set the line width of the scale break.  
   chart1.ChartAreas["ChartArea1"].AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.LineWidth = 2;  

   // Set the color of the scale break.  
   chart1.ChartAreas["ChartArea1"].AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.LineColor = Color.Red;  

   // If all data points are significantly far from zero, the chart will calculate the scale minimum value.  
   chart1.ChartAreas["ChartArea1"].AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.StartFromZero = StartFromZero.Auto;  

   // Set the spacing gap between the lines of the scale break (as a percentage of the Y-axis).  
    chart1.ChartAreas["ChartArea1"].AxisY.ScaleBreakStyle.Spacing = 2;  
}  
```



